{"tid":2317273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宗教是人民「精神上的鴉片」","createTime":"2020-12-08T12:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T16:47:00.000Z","uid":25409,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2c7027d2231b57f05a1f964afb2a03c59ff9c0","tid":2317273,"uid":25409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"稱宗教是人民的鴉片，出自馬克思於1843年創作的《黑格爾法哲學批判》的導言一文，他認為宗教是人民「精神上的鴉片」，這跟共產主義的無神論有關。但馬克思本人並沒有詳細解釋「鴉片」一詞的意涵，大部份學者皆把這解讀成「人類對宗教信仰的依附」。"},{"pid":"1cdd99463d9afb31ad07ad0c4613c29c3a270dd5","tid":2317273,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"雖然我好唔鍾意共產主義<br />\n不過唯物論我係認同<br />\n純粹嘅信仰有時候真係會麻醉人<br />\n令人停止咗思考"},{"pid":"549dfed8a9e3166ff0627e388d57e061587221f8","tid":2317273,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"除咗馬克思之外其實仲有令一套唯物論可以參考<br />\nThe ego and its own - Max Stirner<br />\n佢除咗主張人應該無視道德同宗教之外<br />\n佢甚至覺得所有社會約定俗成嘅概念都可以被無視<br />\n例如統治者、法律、甚至係性別分類<br />\n因為每個人唯一客觀嘅生存意義都係滿足自我慾望<br />\n亦即係話對於任何社會秩序，只要個人意志想反抗都可以選擇拋棄社會嘅枷鎖<br />\n社會上任何普遍存在嘅信念都只係基於無數嘅個體自由選擇嘅結果，而信念本身係唔存在意義。所以每個獨特存在嘅個體都唔需要關心其他個體嘅意願，最後一樣可以作出獨一無二嘅決定。"},{"pid":"aab0674a189d3b9f2b701316aa635907b05c9ace","tid":2317273,"uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"討論未來既新制度，有別於全球資本主義，以及共產主義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7317687/page/9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7317687%2Fpage%2F9&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ad77107f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7317687/page/9</a><br />\n<br />\n共產主義只是一種萬惡的制度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2pjmyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2pjmyW.jpg&h=40b517a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28784168868b28badb022205b2a9d6b4fb89668b","tid":2317273,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aab0674a189d3b9f2b701316aa635907b05c9ace","tid":2317273,"uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"討論未來既新制度，有別於全球資本主義，以及共產主義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7317687/page/9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7317687%2Fpage%2F9&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=ad77107f\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7317687/page/9</a><br />\n<br />\n共產主義只是一種萬惡的制度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2pjmyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2pjmyW.jpg&h=40b517a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"概括嚟講,共產主義：呃傻仔"},{"pid":"25e01eaf95e81b0eef8f84e68130b8973bd1483c","tid":2317273,"uid":12599,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"共產黨本身已經係一個宗教組織"},{"pid":"1d8166793f2fedd5e5fa1976d39cffc9e47f1c2b","tid":2317273,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cdd99463d9afb31ad07ad0c4613c29c3a270dd5","tid":2317273,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:31:50.000Z","msg":"雖然我好唔鍾意共產主義<br />\n不過唯物論我係認同<br />\n純粹嘅信仰有時候真係會麻醉人<br />\n令人停止咗思考"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"唯物論嘅人唔講口齒，無合約精神"},{"pid":"2cffc92dce17a111b8dfce66eab8c62b5dbb44e1","tid":2317273,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"咁又點 咁清醒做咩"}]}